select distinct id_cargo_pengiriman_detail,
no_manifest,
cargo_pengiriman_details.no_pol,
sopir,
sopir_utama,
jenis_pengiriman,
cargo_pengiriman_details.id_kode_kota_asal as asal,
cargo_pengiriman_details.id_kode_kota_tujuan as tujuan,
MAX(message_trackings.id_message_tracking) as last_id_message_tracking,
DATE(cargo_pengiriman_details.created_at) as created from `cargo_pengiriman_details` left join `trucks` on `trucks`.`no_pol` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_pol` left join `trackings` on `trackings`.`no_lmt` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_lmt` left join `message_trackings` on `message_trackings`.`id_message_tracking` = `trackings`.`id_message_tracking` left join `kode_kotas` on `kode_kotas`.`id_kode_kota` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`id_kode_kota_tujuan` where `no_manifest` is not null and `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`id_user` = 2 or `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`id_kode_kota_asal` = '1' group by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_manifest` order by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`created_at` desc
